Kat Korea pun tak banyak kes.

01:03:10.530 --> 01:03:11.660
Bilakah saya akan mati?

01:03:12.760 --> 01:03:14.060
Nah, secara terang-terangan,

01:03:14.760 --> 01:03:18.230
